  <name>AVI MetaEdit</name>
  <summary>Embed, validate, and export AVI files metadata</summary>
  <description>
    <p>AVI MetaEdit is a tool that supports embedding, validating, and exporting of metadata in AVI files.</p>
    <p>This tool can also enforce file structure and metadata recommendations and specifications from U.S. National Archives, Microsoft, and IBM.</p>
    <p>Initially funded by NARA (National Archives and Records Administration) supported by the FADGI; designed and led by AVPreserve; developed by MediaArea.</p>
  </description>
